extendedInfo.description: Join us for the 2013 Open Solutions Client Conference, April 13 - April 17, at the Bellagio in Las Vegas, Nevada, to experience the Power of One! This official conference app provides attendees with a list of sessions, speakers, exhibitors and more. Use the app to build a customized conference schedule, locate session rooms and exhibitors, and connect with your peers. Sessions will cover the following solutions: Raddon Financial Group (RFG), DNA, CUnify, TotalPlus, DNAcreator, DNAappstore, DNAweb, DNAmobile, DNAbillpay, DNApersonalfinance, DNAvoice, Opencheck, Weiland Account Analysis, Velocity, DNAdocument, DNAledger, DNApayables, DNAfixedassets, DNAprofit, DNAgateway, DNA, tMagic, DNAverifast, DNAopendata, DNAreport, DNApublisher, DNAmarket, DNAactivity, DNAcontact, DNAmessage, DNAcreditcard, Weiland BRMedge, Weiland BAweb, and more. Visit http://www.opensolutions.com/about-us/annual-client-conference.aspx for more information. There's Power in Community!
